<div class="home_container">
    <div class="hero_area">
        <div class="bg-box">
            <img src="images/hero-bg.jpg" alt="">
        </div>

        <!-- slider section -->
        <section class="slider_section">
            <div id="customCarousel1" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <div class="container ">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-6 ">
                                    <div class="detail-box">
                                        <h1>
                                            Fast Food Ordering App
                                        </h1>
                                        <p>
                                            HappyFood serves traditional and innovative Japanese dishes. The atmosphere
                                            is casual while the modern and upscale design contributes to a relaxing and
                                            enjoyable dining experience.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="btn-box">
                                            <a href="/order" class="btn1">
                                                Order Now
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item ">
                        <div class="container ">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-6 ">
                                    <div class="detail-box">
                                        <h1>
                                            HappyFood X BurgerKing
                                        </h1>
                                        <p>
                                            Founded in 1954, BURGER KING® is now the largest fast food restaurant chain
                                            in the world. Every day, more than 11 million diners come to BURGER KING®
                                            restaurants around the world to enjoy high quality food, great taste and
                                            affordable prices.
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            Wherever you are, BURGER KING® always keeps the spirit of Taste is King,
                                            satisfying the palate of the most discerning diners when coming to enjoy at
                                            the restaurant. BURGER KING® stores will also uphold BURGER KING®'s motto of
                                            serving "family-friendly meals", as demonstrated by our professionally
                                            trained, fast and friendly service staff. , comfortable space, modern
                                            interior design, fresh and hot dishes, cool drinks and absolute hygiene.
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            BURGER KING®'s motto is that wherever, whenever, we serve the world's best
                                            WHOPPER® cakes to a wide range of discerning customers.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="btn-box">
                                            <a href="/order" class="btn1">
                                                Order Now
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="container ">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-6 ">
                                    <div class="detail-box">
                                        <h1>
                                            HappyFood X KFC
                                        </h1>
                                        <p>
                                            The unique flavors, hospitality and atmosphere of the restaurants remain key
                                            factors in the success of KFC in Vietnam and around the world. In addition,
                                            KFC is highly regarded as a good company through many important social
                                            activities.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="btn-box">
                                            <a href="/order" class="btn1">
                                                Order Now
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container">
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li data-bs-target="#customCarousel1" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true"
                            aria-label="Slide 1"></li>
                        <li data-bs-target="#customCarousel1" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></li>
                        <li data-bs-target="#customCarousel1" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>
        <!-- end slider section -->
    </div>

    <!-- offer section -->

    <section class="offer_section layout_padding-bottom">
        <div class="offer_container">
            <div class="container ">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6  ">
                        <div class="box ">
                            <div class="img-box">
                                <img src="images/o1.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="detail-box">
                                <h5>
                                    Tasty Thursdays
                                </h5>
                                <h6>
                                    <span>20%</span> Off
                                </h6>
                                <a href="/order">
                                    Order Now <i class="ms-1 fa-solid fa-cart-plus"></i>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6  ">
                        <div class="box ">
                            <div class="img-box">
                                <img src="images/o2.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="detail-box">
                                <h5>
                                    Pizza Days
                                </h5>
                                <h6>
                                    <span>15%</span> Off
                                </h6>
                                <a href="/order">
                                    Order Now <i class="ms-1 fa-solid fa-cart-plus"></i>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- end offer section -->

    <!-- food section -->

    <section class="food_section layout_padding-bottom">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="heading_container heading_center">
                <h2>
                    Our Menu
                </h2>
            </div>

            <ul class="filters_menu">
                <li class="active" data-filter="*">All</li>
                <li data-filter=".burger">Burger</li>
                <li data-filter=".pizza">Pizza</li>
                <li data-filter=".pasta">Pasta</li>
                <li data-filter=".fries">Fries</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="filters-content">
                <div class="row grid">
                    {{#each product}}
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 all pizza" id="{{this._id}}-item">
                        <div class="box shadow">
                            <div>
                                <div class="img-box">
                                    <img id="{{this._id}}-image" src="../../uploads/{{this.image}}"
                                        class="card-img-top" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <div class="mb-3 overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 100px;">
                                        <h5>
                                            {{this.name}}
                                        </h5>
                                        <p>
                                            {{this.desc}}
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="options">
                                        <h5 class="fw-bolder pt-2">
                                            $<span class="" data-id="{{this._id}}">{{this.price}}</span>
                                        </h5>
                                        <div class="d-flex flex-row">
                                            <a class="text-white" href="/product/show/{{this._id}}">
                                                <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                                            </a>
                                            <a class="text-white ms-3" href="/cart/add-to-cart/{{this._id}}">
                                                <i class="fa-solid fa-cart-plus"></i>
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {{/each}}



                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-box">
                <a href="/order">
                    View More
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- end food section -->

    <!-- about section -->

    <section class="about_section layout_padding">
        <div class="container  ">

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 ">
                    <div class="img-box">
                        <img src="images/about-img.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="detail-box">
                        <div class="heading_container">
                            <h2>
                                We Are HappyFood
                            </h2>
                        </div>
                        <p>
                            HF stands for HappyFood. One of the new forms of fast food system in Vietnam market. Founded
                            by a group of young students with enthusiasm and youthful energy. Specializes in processing
                            and manufacturing delicious, nutritious and cheap dinner dishes with quality and affordable
                            prices... 100% raw materials are clean ingredients, of clear origin, certified and licensed
                            by the Ministry of Health. permission.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Based on the natural needs of people, aiming to serve wholeheartedly for customers who need
                            to eat at night, but are afraid to leave the house, or can't find a suitable place to eat at
                            night, and can't find good food. eat your favorite food,.. Now, you don't need to worry
                            about it anymore. We have HappyFood ready when you need it, giving you energy to work in
                            just 30 minutes. With a team of professional shipper staff, fast, delicious and safe
                            processing, .. We hope to bring you the highest satisfaction. Unique taste, friendly service
                            style, wholeheartedly for customers and warm and cozy atmosphere are the three main keys to
                            the success of HappyFood.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#">
                            Read More
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- end about section -->

